posting_body: ['Unit Availability: August 3, 2022', 'Moments away from Hollywood Boulevard, Cherokee Villas is an ideal place to call home.', "You'll be close to a wide variety of shops and upscale eateries along with commuter-friendly freeways and the Metro Station.", 'Our studio apartments come equipped with stylish hardwood style flooring, a breakfast nook, and kitchen appliances.', ' We also offer a convenient laundry facility and controlled access.', 'Living at Cherokee Villas in Hollywood, CA means being in the center of it all.', 'APARTMENT AMENITIES:', '-- Chandelier', '-- Breakfast Nook', '-- Refrigerator', '-- Custom Paint (In Select Units)', '-- Hardwood Floors', '-- Stove/Oven', 'COMMUNITY AMENITIES:', '-- Controlled Access/Gated', '-- Laundry Facility', '-- Street Parking or Parking Garage Across The Street $144 Per Month', 'CONTACT US:', 'show contact info', "We're here to help every step of the way.", 'Call and make an appointment with us today!', 'On-site Tours Available By Appointment.']
